    "name": "Barbarian Dedication",
    "prerequisite": "Constitution +2; Strength +2",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You become trained in Athletics; if you were already trained in Athletics, you instead become trained in a skill of your choice. You become trained in barbarian class DC. You can use the Rage action. While raging, you take a \u20131 penalty to AC. Choose an instinct as you would if you were a barbarian. You have that instinct for all purposes, but you don\u2019t gain any of the other abilities it grants. If that instinct has anathema, you\u2019re bound by them.",
    "traits": [
